worldview_rules.v1.json — Schema + Semantics
1. Purpose of this file (machine-side)
This file answers, in code:
What kinds of claims are allowed?
What kinds of claims are forbidden?
How causality may be expressed
How uncertainty must be expressed
What language is categorically illegal
This file is consulted by:
Interpreter (pre-generation)
QA (post-generation)
Editorial gate (final check)
If this file is missing or invalid → pipeline must fail.

